          "mount": "fixed",
          "linked": 0
        },
        {
          "weaponId": "torpedo_med",
          "mount": "fixed",
          "linked": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Citadel Station",
      "desc": "Corporate headquarters station and the strategic objective of most deep-space territorial wars. She's a fortress, a factory, a marketplace, and a symbol of territorial control all in one. Her defences can hold off a small fleet, her markets set commodity prices for entire regions, and her destruction would reshape the economic landscape of known space. Wars are fought over these, and the wars never really end.",
      "notes": "Stationary. Corporate HQ. Extensive defences. Strategic objective.",
      "size": 26,
      "loco": "none",
      "toughLevel": 4,
      "armourLevel": 3,
